@startuml sequence_pipeline
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Hardened request pipeline

actor User
participant "TLS termination" as TLS
participant "Security headers" as SH
participant "Rate limiter" as RL
participant "Auth cookie reader" as AUTH
participant "Endpoint handler" as EP
participant "Validation guards" as V
participant "DbContext (global filter)" as CTX
database "Postgres" as DB

User -> TLS: HTTPS
TLS -> SH: plain HTTP inside process
SH -> RL: +HSTS, CSP, nosniff
RL -> AUTH: under policy budget?
AUTH -> EP: ctx.User populated
EP -> V: validate request
V -> CTX: SELECT (scoped by OwnerUserId)
CTX -> DB: SQL with owner filter
DB --> CTX: rows (same user only)
CTX --> EP: dto
EP --> User: 200 + security headers

@enduml
